---
---

<footer class="footer" data-mode="dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-statement reveal">
      <p class="footer-statement-text">
        Diseño con proceso para organizaciones<br />
        que no pueden permitirse el <em class="footer-italic">desorden</em><span class="text-accent">.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-divider reveal-line"></div>

    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <img src="/brand/proma-wordmark-light.svg" alt="proma" class="footer-logo" />
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="#servicios">Diagnóstico & Consultoría</a></li>
          <li><a href="#servicios">Packaging</a></li>
          <li><a href="#servicios">Branding</a></li>
          <li><a href="#servicios">Web & Aplicaciones</a></li>
          <li><a href="#servicios">Mantenimiento & Retainer</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <p class="type-label footer-claim">
          Human-Led.<br />System-Driven.<br />Intelligence-Enhanced.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col footer-contact">
        <a href="mailto:hola@pro.ma" class="footer-email" data-cursor-hover>hola@pro.ma</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="type-mono-sm footer-legal">
        © 2026 pro.ma Studio · Buenos Aires · LATAM
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: var(--proma-navy-900);
    color: var(--proma-cream-100);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--proma-navy-700);
    padding: clamp(80px, 10vh, 120px) 0 var(--space-10);
  }

  .footer-statement {
    margin-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vh, 80px);
  }

  .footer-statement-text {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .footer-italic {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--proma-terra-500);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .text-accent {
    color: var(--proma-terra-500);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .footer-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--proma-navy-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .footer-logo {
    height: 24px;
    width: auto;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .footer-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.35;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: var(--proma-terra-500);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .footer-claim {
    color: var(--proma-terra-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .footer-email {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.35;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .footer-email:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: var(--proma-terra-500);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  .footer-legal {
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
